  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomized controlled clinical trial will estimate the eradication efficacy of different&#xD;
      therapy for Helicobacter pylori treatment. The completion of this trial will expand new&#xD;
      therapy for the treatment of Helicobacter pylori, which can not only ensure clinical&#xD;
      efficacy, but also reduce the use of antibiotics.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
